food.name: Jordan Sub Sandwich, WG
food.description: Our Jordan sub is the ultimate deli hoagie, and every ingredient is important to its success. For ours, we combine a beautiful made from scratch whole grain French bread with our tasty ham and turkey deli meats and reduced-fat cheese. It's an over-the-top, delicious sub.

food.name: Shoestring French Fries
food.description: These specially-seasoned baked fries are our healthy take on the traditional (and not so healthy) french fry. Potatoes have more potassium than bananas and are a healthy food for kids. We bake ours until they're golden brown and let the kids dunk them in their favorite sauce. Hello nutrition!

food.name: Teriyaki Chicken w/ Noodles
food.description: Yes, this dish combines succulent pieces of skinless, boneless, chicken breasts with a thick, sweetened sauce redolent with hints of dried red chilies, brown sugar, molasses, clover honey, pineapple juice, and a touch of spice. The combination delights the sense & teases the taste buds! We serve our teriyaki chicken with whole grain noodles!

food.name: Side Salad
food.description: Sure, salads are healthy. Leafy greens are vitamin-rich! But when was the last time you saw a room full of kids energetically munching down salads? Just visit one of our lunchrooms when this item is served. You'll be in for a treat!

food.name: Applesauce
food.description: No berry or fruit-flavored imposters here -- just the real stuff. Pure apples. Our applesauce has an intense, fresh apple taste bound up in a homemade texture.
